Our house!

01:14:59.960 --> 01:15:02.155
<i>Come on. Whoo-hoo!
Come on.</i>

01:15:02.229 --> 01:15:04.163
Come on.
We gotta go!

01:15:04.231 --> 01:15:06.825
Whoo!

01:15:06.901 --> 01:15:08.892
Come on!

01:15:09.970 --> 01:15:11.870
We gotta go. Clem?

01:15:11.939 --> 01:15:14.840
We gotta go.

01:15:14.909 --> 01:15:16.809
Aah! Come on!

01:15:16.877 --> 01:15:19.072
No!
This is a really bad time
for this!

01:15:19.146 --> 01:15:22.081
Get off me! Oh, God!

01:15:22.149 --> 01:15:25.084
I don't even know
where we're going.
It's gonna be fun. Come on.

01:15:25.152 --> 01:15:27.677
It's the best place.
No, this way.
No, this way.

01:15:27.755 --> 01:15:32.385
No, no, no. This way.
You're no help at all.

01:15:32.459 --> 01:15:35.189
What's wrong with you?

01:15:35.262 --> 01:15:38.425
Let go of me, Joel!

01:15:50.444 --> 01:15:52.071
I like watching you work,
Howard.

01:15:56.183 --> 01:15:58.674
I guess, uh...

01:15:58.752 --> 01:16:01.550
I guess I'll go out
for... for some air,

01:16:01.622 --> 01:16:03.613
if nobody minds.

01:16:03.691 --> 01:16:06.888
It looks like you have everything
under control here.

01:16:06.961 --> 01:16:08.895
Yeah, that's, uh...

01:16:08.963 --> 01:16:10.897
<i>that's fine.</i>

01:16:20.608 --> 01:16:23.600
<i>Do you like quotes, Howard?</i>

01:16:24.678 --> 01:16:26.612
What do you mean?

01:16:26.680 --> 01:16:29.376
<i>Oh, you know,
like famous quotes?</i>

01:16:29.450 --> 01:16:31.611
I find reading them inspirational,

01:16:31.685 --> 01:16:35.587
and in my reading,
I've come across some
I thought you might like too.

01:16:35.656 --> 01:16:39.319
Oh, well, I...
I'd love to hear some.

01:16:39.393 --> 01:16:41.827
<i>There's one that goes,</i>

01:16:41.896 --> 01:16:45.388
"Blessed are the forgetful,
for they get the better
even of their blunders."

01:16:45.466 --> 01:16:47.400
<i>That's Nietzsche, right?
Yeah.</i>

01:16:47.468 --> 01:16:50.460
And here I thought I could tell you
something you didn't know.
Oh, no.

01:16:50.537 --> 01:16:53.665
It's... It's a good quote.
I'm happy we both know it.

01:16:53.741 --> 01:16:56.733
Yeah. Oh, and there's
this other one I like.

01:16:56.810 --> 01:16:59.643
It's by Pope Alexander,
and it goes...

01:16:59.713 --> 01:17:02.181
<i>Alexander Pope?
Oh, yeah.</i>

01:17:02.249 --> 01:17:04.183
<i>Yeah, shit.</i>

01:17:04.251 --> 01:17:08.085
<i>It's just that I told myself
not to say "Pope Alexander"
and sound like a dope,</i>

01:17:08.155 --> 01:17:10.146
and then I go ahead and say it.

01:17:10.224 --> 01:17:13.751
It's no big deal.
You're such a sweetheart.

01:17:15.596 --> 01:17:19.532
<i>The quote goes, "How happy is
the blameless vestal's lot?</i>

01:17:20.768 --> 01:17:23.862
<i>"The world forgetting,
by the world forgot.</i>

01:17:23.938 --> 01:17:28.272
<i>"Eternal sunshine
of the spotless mind.</i>

01:17:28.342 --> 01:17:31.903
<i>Each prayer accepted
and each wish resigned."</i>

01:17:31.979 --> 01:17:36.939
<i>I want to be
a great big, huge elephant...</i>

01:17:37.017 --> 01:17:39.485
<i>with a huge trunk like that.</i>

01:17:40.888 --> 01:17:43.823
Clem? Clementine?

01:17:43.891 --> 01:17:46.860
I haven't heard that one.
It's lovely.

01:17:46.927 --> 01:17:49.896
I just thought it would
be appropriate, maybe.

01:17:54.568 --> 01:17:58.231
I really admire
the work you do, Howard.

01:17:58.305 --> 01:18:00.796
I don't mean to be so familiar.
Oh, it's fine. It's fine.

01:18:00.874 --> 01:18:03.399
I- I- I- I- I...
I'm happy to hear...

01:18:07.181 --> 01:18:10.173
I'm sorry.

01:18:14.221 --> 01:18:16.553
I've loved you
for a very long time.

01:18:19.827 --> 01:18:22.159
<i>I shouldn't have said that.
Oh, Mary, no.</i>

01:18:22.229 --> 01:18:25.460
<i>It's... You're a wonderful girl.</i>

01:18:25.532 --> 01:18:29.229
But I... You know,
I have a wife and kids.

01:18:29.303 --> 01:18:31.237
You know
I have a wife and kids.

01:18:31.305 --> 01:18:33.239
<i>Oh, Mary.</i>

01:18:35.376 --> 01:18:38.243
Oh, Mary, we can't do this.

01:18:48.255 --> 01:18:50.246
Oh, whoa.

01:18:54.695 --> 01:18:57.960
Well, good morning,
Mrs. Mierzwiak.

01:19:05.372 --> 01:19:07.363
<i>What?
Oh, my God!</i>

01:19:07.441 --> 01:19:09.966
<i>Who is it?</i>

01:19:14.381 --> 01:19:16.747
Uh...

01:19:22.423 --> 01:19:25.654
Thank you, Stan.
Thanks a lot.

01:19:29.396 --> 01:19:32.422
Hollis. Hollis!

01:19:32.499 --> 01:19:34.933
<i>Hollis!</i>

01:19:35.002 --> 01:19:37.163
Wait. Wait, wait, wait.
Hollis.

01:19:38.472 --> 01:19:40.963
- I knew it, Howard.
- Hollis, it didn't start out
to be like this.

01:19:41.041 --> 01:19:44.408
I came here to work.
Hollis, this is a one-time mistake!

01:19:44.478 --> 01:19:46.946
<i>I'm a stupid girl
with a stupid crush!
Yeah.</i>

01:19:47.014 --> 01:19:49.505
I swear I basically
forced him into it!

01:19:50.717 --> 01:19:53.345
Don't be a monster, Howard.
Tell the girl.

01:19:56.023 --> 01:19:58.753
Tell me what?

01:19:58.826 --> 01:20:00.817
Oh, you poor kid.

01:20:01.829 --> 01:20:03.922
You can have him.

01:20:03.997 --> 01:20:05.931
You did.

01:20:14.441 --> 01:20:16.432
What?

01:20:20.247 --> 01:20:22.238
Oh, uh,

01:20:27.254 --> 01:20:30.849
we have a history.

01:20:30.924 --> 01:20:33.484
I'm sorry.
Y-You wanted the procedure.

01:20:33.560 --> 01:20:35.721
You...

01:20:35.796 --> 01:20:38.287
You wanted it done...

01:20:38.365 --> 01:20:41.664
so you could get past, uh...

01:20:43.370 --> 01:20:45.361
You could... Yeah.

01:20:46.840 --> 01:20:51.800
Um, I have to, uh,
finish the work in there.

01:20:51.879 --> 01:20:53.870
It's almost morning.

01:20:55.082 --> 01:20:57.073
We'll talk later.

01:20:58.085 --> 01:21:00.019
Okay?

01:21:10.998 --> 01:21:12.932
<i>Hey.</i>

01:21:16.870 --> 01:21:18.861
Let me give you a lift home.

01:21:28.448 --> 01:21:31.008
Fuck this thing. Damn it.

01:21:31.084 --> 01:21:34.679
Hi.
Hi.

01:21:34.755 --> 01:21:38.691
Didn't figure you'd show your face
around me again.

01:21:38.759 --> 01:21:41.990
I guess I thought
you were... humiliated.

01:21:42.062 --> 01:21:44.030
You did run away,
after all.

01:21:44.097 --> 01:21:46.861
<i>I just needed to see ya.</i>

01:21:46.934 --> 01:21:49.232
Yeah?

01:21:49.303 --> 01:21:52.033
I'd like to, um,

01:21:52.105 --> 01:21:55.074
take you out or something.

01:21:55.142 --> 01:21:57.702
You're married.

01:21:57.778 --> 01:22:00.212
Not yet. Not married.

01:22:00.280 --> 01:22:02.214
No, I'm not married, no.

01:22:02.282 --> 01:22:05.308
Look, man,
I'm telling you right off the bat
I'm high maintenance,

01:22:05.385 --> 01:22:09.947
so I'm not gonna tiptoe
around your marriage...

01:22:10.023 --> 01:22:12.355
or whatever it is
you've got going there.

01:22:12.426 --> 01:22:15.554
If you wanna be with me,
you're with me.

01:22:15.629 --> 01:22:17.790
Okay.

01:22:17.864 --> 01:22:20.765
Too many guys think I'm a concept,
or I complete them,

01:22:20.834 --> 01:22:23.632
or I'm gonna make them alive.

01:22:23.704 --> 01:22:27.333
But I'm just a fucked-up girl
who's looking for
my own peace of mind.

01:22:27.407 --> 01:22:32.071
Don't assign me yours.
I remember that speech
really well.

01:22:32.145 --> 01:22:35.637
I had you pegged, didn't I?
You had the whole
human race pegged.

01:22:35.716 --> 01:22:37.707
Hmm. Probably.

01:22:39.886 --> 01:22:42.184
I still thought you were
gonna save my life,

01:22:42.256 --> 01:22:44.190
even after that.

01:22:44.258 --> 01:22:47.659
Mmm. I know.

01:22:49.997 --> 01:22:51.988
It would be different...

01:22:53.133 --> 01:22:55.533
if we could just give it
another go around.

01:22:59.506 --> 01:23:01.872
Remember me.

01:23:01.942 --> 01:23:03.933
Try your best.

01:23:06.280 --> 01:23:08.214
Maybe we can.

01:23:39.479 --> 01:23:42.414
Okay, so just tell me
what you remember,

01:23:42.482 --> 01:23:45.076
and, uh, then we'll
take it from there.

01:23:45.152 --> 01:23:47.382
Okay.

01:23:47.454 --> 01:23:50.355
I liked you immediately.

01:23:50.424 --> 01:23:52.915
<i>You didn't
come on to me at all.</i>

01:23:52.993 --> 01:23:55.985
<i>I liked that.</i>

01:23:56.063 --> 01:23:59.032
<i>I was so tongue-tied
around you at first.</i>

01:23:59.099 --> 01:24:01.761
<i>I wanted you to think
I was smart.</i>

01:24:02.969 --> 01:24:05.301
I couldn't wait
to come to work.

01:24:05.372 --> 01:24:08.864
I had these fantasies
of us being married...

01:24:08.942 --> 01:24:12.309
and having kids and... just...

01:24:12.379 --> 01:24:15.075
<i>Oh, Howie, I can't do this.</i>

01:24:15.148 --> 01:24:17.742
<i>We agreed it's for the best, Mary.</i>

01:24:17.818 --> 01:24:20.286
<i>Yeah, I know.</i>

01:24:20.354 --> 01:24:22.288
<i>Oh, God.</i>

01:24:22.622 --> 01:24:24.715
I'll take the bottom and you...
Uh-uh-uh! No, no, no. Here.

01:24:24.791 --> 01:24:26.725
I can take that.
So you want me to carry that?

01:24:26.793 --> 01:24:29.284
Help me with that.
Can you get the cooler?
Honey, the cooler is...

01:24:29.363 --> 01:24:31.957
That's light, huh?
Oh, I can get that.
You can get it.

01:24:32.032 --> 01:24:33.966
No, no, no, no!

01:24:34.034 --> 01:24:36.195
Don't take anything.
I can take the plane.

01:24:36.269 --> 01:24:39.261
Put the thing up.
Put the gate back up.

01:24:41.508 --> 01:24:44.238
<i>This is the day we met.</i>

01:24:44.311 --> 01:24:47.508
<i>You were down by the surf.
I could just make you out
in the distance.</i>

01:24:47.581 --> 01:24:49.708
<i>I remember being drawn to you
even then.</i>

01:24:49.783 --> 01:24:53.913
<i>I thought, "Wow, how odd.
I'm drawn to someone's back."</i>

01:24:55.689 --> 01:24:58.852
<i>You were in that orange sweatshirt
that I would come to know so well...</i>

01:24:58.925 --> 01:25:00.893
<i>and even hate, eventually.</i>

01:25:00.961 --> 01:25:04.954
At the time I thought,
"How cool! An orange sweatshirt."

01:25:05.031 --> 01:25:07.761
Hi there.

01:25:07.834 --> 01:25:09.768
Hi.

01:25:09.836 --> 01:25:12.771
I saw you sitting over here...

01:25:12.839 --> 01:25:14.773
by yourself,

01:25:14.841 --> 01:25:17.742
and I thought, "Thank God.

01:25:17.811 --> 01:25:20.609
Someone normal
who doesn't know how to interact
at these things either."

01:25:20.680 --> 01:25:22.807
Yeah.

01:25:22.883 --> 01:25:25.909
I don't ever know what to say.

01:25:25.986 --> 01:25:28.716
I'm Clementine.

01:25:28.789 --> 01:25:31.952
Can I borrow a piece
of your chicken?

01:25:32.025 --> 01:25:34.255
And then you just took it...

01:25:34.327 --> 01:25:36.852
without waiting for an answer.

01:25:40.400 --> 01:25:42.891
It was so intimate,

01:25:42.969 --> 01:25:46.097
like we were already lovers.

01:25:46.173 --> 01:25:48.971
I'm Joel.

01:25:49.042 --> 01:25:51.203
Hi, Joel.

01:25:51.278 --> 01:25:54.509
So, no jokes about my name.

01:25:54.581 --> 01:25:59.041
You mean like...

01:25:59.119 --> 01:26:01.610
Huckleberry Hound,
that sort of thing?

01:26:01.688 --> 01:26:03.713
Yeah. Like that.

01:26:03.790 --> 01:26:05.724
Oh, no jokes. No jokes.

01:26:05.792 --> 01:26:09.523
One of my favorite things when I was a kid
was my Huckleberry Hound doll.

01:26:09.596 --> 01:26:11.587
<i>Oh.</i>

01:26:13.533 --> 01:26:15.865
I think your name is magical.

01:26:18.772 --> 01:26:21.070
This is it, Joel.

01:26:21.141 --> 01:26:23.336
It's gonna be gone soon.

01:26:25.479 --> 01:26:27.811
I know.

01:26:27.881 --> 01:26:29.815
What do we do?

01:26:32.219 --> 01:26:34.710
Enjoy it.

01:26:51.371 --> 01:26:53.669
You married?
No.

01:26:53.740 --> 01:26:56.368
Let's move into
this neighborhood!

01:26:56.443 --> 01:26:58.343
I do sort of live
with someone though.

01:26:58.411 --> 01:27:01.778
Male or female?
What?

01:27:01.848 --> 01:27:04.282
Female. Female.

01:27:06.419 --> 01:27:09.911
At least I'm not barking
up the wrong tree.

01:27:12.692 --> 01:27:16.685
You know these people?
No, of course not.
Come on.

01:27:17.697 --> 01:27:19.631
They might have a dog.

01:27:19.699 --> 01:27:23.362
There's no dog.

01:27:23.436 --> 01:27:25.427
What are you doing?

01:27:25.505 --> 01:27:28.770
<i>It's freezing out.
I can't believe this.</i>

01:27:28.842 --> 01:27:31.811
Hoo-hoo!

01:27:31.878 --> 01:27:35.712
<i>- Clementine!
- There we go. Whoo-hoo!</i>

01:27:42.455 --> 01:27:45.049
Come on, man.
The water's fine.

01:27:45.125 --> 01:27:48.253
Nobody's coming here tonight.
Believe me.

01:27:50.997 --> 01:27:52.931
It's dark.

01:27:52.999 --> 01:27:56.992
So, uh, what's
your girlfriend's name?

01:27:57.070 --> 01:28:00.301
Naomi, but we're not really...
I mean...

01:28:00.373 --> 01:28:02.773
We're...
Whatever.

01:28:02.842 --> 01:28:06.938
<i>So this is great.
Now I can look for, um,
candles, matches...</i>

01:28:07.013 --> 01:28:09.481
<i>and the liquor cabinet.</i>

01:28:09.549 --> 01:28:12.814
<i>Oh, God.</i>

01:28:17.390 --> 01:28:19.255
I think we should go.

01:28:19.326 --> 01:28:21.920
There's no phone line.
What?

01:28:21.995 --> 01:28:24.156
<i>I think we should go.
Why?</i>

01:28:24.230 --> 01:28:26.824
It's our house...
just for tonight.

01:28:26.900 --> 01:28:29.869
We are "David and Ruth Laskin."

01:28:31.004 --> 01:28:33.438
<i>Which one do you want to be?
Uh...</i>

01:28:33.506 --> 01:28:36.998
I prefer to be Ruth,
but I can be flexible.

01:28:38.511 --> 01:28:41.844
What are you do...

01:28:41.915 --> 01:28:44.145
Alcohol!
Oh, boy.

01:28:44.217 --> 01:28:46.811
So, are you okay with wine?

01:28:46.886 --> 01:28:49.548
I don't know.
Well, you choose the wine.

01:28:49.623 --> 01:28:53.855
I'm gonna go find the bedroom
and slip into something more... Ruth.

01:28:57.263 --> 01:29:00.027
<i>I'm Ruth-less at the moment.
I really should go.</i>

01:29:01.768 --> 01:29:04.896
I've gotta catch my ride.

01:29:06.740 --> 01:29:09.231
<i>So go.</i>

01:29:09.309 --> 01:29:11.402
I did.

01:29:11.478 --> 01:29:14.345
<i>I thought maybe you were a nut,</i>

01:29:14.414 --> 01:29:17.212
<i>but you were exciting.</i>

01:29:18.318 --> 01:29:20.252
<i>I wish you'd stayed.</i>

01:29:20.320 --> 01:29:23.016
I wish I'd stayed too.
Now I wish I'd stayed.

01:29:23.089 --> 01:29:26.149
I wish I'd done a lot of things.

01:29:26.226 --> 01:29:28.558
Oh, God, I wish I had...

01:29:32.532 --> 01:29:35.660
I wish I'd stayed. I do.

01:29:35.735 --> 01:29:40.297
<i>Well, I came back downstairs,
and you were gone.
I walked out. I walked out the door.</i>

01:29:40.373 --> 01:29:43.206
<i>Why?
I don't know.
I felt like a scared little kid.</i>

01:29:43.276 --> 01:29:46.609
I was like...
It was above my head.
I don't know.

01:29:46.680 --> 01:29:48.614
<i>You were scared?</i>

01:29:48.682 --> 01:29:50.616
Yeah.

01:29:51.651 --> 01:29:54.279
Thought you knew that
about me.

01:29:54.354 --> 01:29:58.347
<i>I ran back to the bonfire,
trying to outrun my humiliation, I think.</i>

01:29:58.425 --> 01:30:02.054
<i>Was it something I said?
Yeah.</i>

01:30:04.831 --> 01:30:07.231
You said, "So go"...

01:30:07.300 --> 01:30:09.768
with such disdain, you know?

01:30:09.836 --> 01:30:12.464
<i>Oh, I'm sorry.
It's okay.</i>

01:30:18.044 --> 01:30:19.978
<i>Joely?</i>

01:30:20.046 --> 01:30:22.913
What if you stayed this time?

01:30:25.585 --> 01:30:28.213
I walked out the door.

01:30:28.288 --> 01:30:30.222
There's no memory left.

01:30:30.290 --> 01:30:33.418
Come back and make up
a good-bye, at least.

01:30:33.493 --> 01:30:35.427
Let's pretend we had one.

01:30:46.539 --> 01:30:49.030
Bye, Joel.

01:30:49.109 --> 01:30:51.043
I love you.

01:30:51.111 --> 01:30:55.377
Meet me in Montauk.

01:30:59.052 --> 01:31:03.250
<i>I didn't crash the plane.
The plane crashed.
I didn't crash the plane.</i>

01:31:03.323 --> 01:31:07.419
<i>You were operating the plane
with the remote control,
and then it crashed.</i>

01:31:07.494 --> 01:31:09.826
<i>It was fucking windy.
Come on, man.</i>

01:31:09.896 --> 01:31:11.864
<i>You're stoned, and you're driving.</i>

01:31:11.931 --> 01:31:14.491
<i>Yeah, the pot balances it out.
The pot brings you back up.</i>

01:31:14.567 --> 01:31:17.092
<i>That's why I smoke it.
If I'm going to be drinking,
then I'll smoke it.</i>

01:31:17.170 --> 01:31:20.799
<i>It does.
That's a medical fact.</i>

01:31:20.874 --> 01:31:23.308
<i>It was proven
on the Science Network.</i>

01:31:23.376 --> 01:31:25.810
<i>Honey, just watch the road.
I can't see shit.</i>

01:31:28.381 --> 01:31:31.373
I saw you talking
to somebody pretty.

01:31:31.451 --> 01:31:34.284
<i>She was nice.
Yeah, man. Who was that?</i>

01:31:36.389 --> 01:31:39.688
She was, um, just a girl.

01:31:47.200 --> 01:31:50.067
Okay.

01:32:25.572 --> 01:32:28.336
So I gotta...
I gotta drop the van off.

01:32:28.408 --> 01:32:30.501
<i>Thanks, Stan. Thanks.</i>

01:32:30.577 --> 01:32:33.910
We'll talk.

01:33:51.925 --> 01:33:53.916
Hey!

01:33:54.994 --> 01:33:56.928
Hey.

01:33:58.398 --> 01:34:01.128
You got a lot
of your stuff there, I see.
Yeah, that's right. My stuff.

01:34:01.200 --> 01:34:04.636
<i>I take it you're not coming back.
I wouldn't come back if I was you either.</i>

01:34:04.704 --> 01:34:08.435
Do you swear you didn't know?
I-I swear.

01:34:08.508 --> 01:34:12.103
