01:37:06.252 --> 01:37:08.186
last night.

01:37:08.254 --> 01:37:10.245
That's better.

01:37:13.359 --> 01:37:17.557
<i>This is weird.
To all patients
of Dr. Howard Mierzwiak.</i>

01:37:17.630 --> 01:37:21.122
<i>My name is Mary Svevo.
"We've met,
but you don't remember me.</i>

01:37:21.200 --> 01:37:25.637
