01:37:32.945 --> 01:37:36.540
<i>My name is Clementine Kruczynski.</i>

01:37:36.616 --> 01:37:39.346
<i>I'm here to erase Joel Barish.</i>

01:37:39.418 --> 01:37:41.648
What is this?
I don't know.

01:37:41.721 --> 01:37:46.317
<i>He's boring.
Is that enough reason
to erase someone?</i>

01:37:46.392 --> 01:37:50.089
<i>I've been thinking lately
how I was before and how I am now,</i>

01:37:50.163 --> 01:37:52.097
<i>and it's like he changed me.</i>

01:37:52.165 --> 01:37:55.931
<i>I feel like I'm always pissy now.
