No! Get the fuck away!

01:39:25.024 --> 01:39:27.288
Joel Barish.

01:39:27.360 --> 01:39:30.124
<i>Hey, Clementine.
Hey.</i>

01:39:30.196 --> 01:39:33.427
Nice to see you. Yeah.

01:39:34.433 --> 01:39:36.367
