01:39:54.687 --> 01:39:56.678
<i>Hi.
because she would pronounce...</i>

01:39:56.756 --> 01:39:59.520
<i>library "libary."
Hi.</i>

01:39:59.592 --> 01:40:02.720
<i>Libary. Libary.</i>

01:40:02.795 --> 01:40:04.729
Look what I found.

01:40:04.797 --> 01:40:09.131
<i>I think if there's
a truly seductive quality
