01:40:09.201 --> 01:40:12.864
<i>it's that her personality promises
to take you out of the mundane.</i>

01:40:14.240 --> 01:40:16.572
<i>You made me look skinny.</i>

01:40:16.642 --> 01:40:19.202
<i>Amazing, burning meteorite...</i>

01:40:19.278 --> 01:40:23.578
<i>will carry you to another world
where things are exciting.</i>

01:40:23.649 --> 01:40:26.675
<i>But what you quickly learn
is that...</i>

01:40:26.752 --> 01:40:29.585
<i>it's really an elaborate ruse.</i>

01:40:29.655 --> 01:40:31.646
I'm sorry I yelled at you.

01:40:33.259 --> 01:40:35.989
<i>It's okay.
So flashy
in a kind of obvious way.</i>

01:40:37.697 --> 01:40:40.257
<i>But still, it seduces you.
Joel, I really like you.</i>

01:40:40.333 --> 01:40:42.563
