mean things about you.

01:40:42.635 --> 01:40:47.095
<i>- Let me turn this off, okay?
- Hey, it's... it's only fair.</i>

01:40:48.441 --> 01:40:50.409
<i>Where's the real Clementine?</i>

01:40:50.476 --> 01:40:53.604
<i>I mean, the whole thing with the hair...
