01:41:07.293 --> 01:41:12.595
<i>No, I don't think her sex
is... motivated.</i>

01:41:12.665 --> 01:41:15.657
<i>I saw it clearly
the last night we were together.</i>

01:41:15.735 --> 01:41:19.136
<i>It wasn't sex.
