01:41:19.205 --> 01:41:22.265
Hey. Sorry.
I thought there was more.

01:41:22.341 --> 01:41:26.004
<i>The only way Clem thinks
she can get people to like her...</i>

01:41:26.078 --> 01:41:28.911
<i>is to fuck 'em...</i>

01:41:28.981 --> 01:41:33.213
<i>or at least dangle the possibility
