about you.</i>

01:41:44.296 --> 01:41:47.197
- Because I don't.
- I know.

01:41:47.266 --> 01:41:50.497
<i>Because it really hurts me
that you said that
because I don't do that.</i>

01:41:50.569 --> 01:41:53.663
<i>I'm so sorry.
I'm sorry about all this.
I'm gonna... go.</i>

01:41:53.739 --> 01:41:58.540
