01:42:50.663 --> 01:42:53.359
<i>Okay.
Really?</i>

01:42:53.432 --> 01:42:57.562
<i>I'm not a concept, Joel.
I'm just a fucked-up girl who's looking
for my own peace of mind.</i>

01:42:57.636 --> 01:43:01.572
- I'm not perfect.
- I can't see anything
that I don't like about you.

01:43:01.640 --> 01:43:04.336
Right now I can't.
